channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Oklahoma Sooners Unveil 1946-56 Throwback Uniforms
item.description: Oklahoma will celebrate the 100th season of Gaylord Family-Oklahoma Memorial Stadium this fall by wearing 1946-56 throwback uniforms against Houston on Sept. 7.

item.description: Travis Scott has found himself in legal trouble once again ... the rapper was arrested in Paris after fighting his bodyguard in a hotel, TMZ has confirmed. Paris prosecutors tell us ... police were called to the George V luxury hotel early Friday…

item.title: Colourful Player Numbers on Caps for MLB’s 2024 Players’ Weekend
item.description: Next weekend is Players’ Weekend across Major League Baseball. The series of games played from August 16-18 will be the first time MLB will host a Players’ Weekend since 2019. As part of this year’s celebration, each player’s uniform number will be worn on the right side of their cap
